content.title: Not Me!
content.body:
No, I can't allow this. I won't allow this! I will not DIE here, in this HOVEL!
I must get back to my city. Surely there's something here that I can use to get back... there must be... there has to be....
I have to get back… I have to… get… back…
I should've joined that other group when I had the chance...
